A traditional stew originating from Georgia, adapted with a Ukrainian touch. It features tender pieces of pork slow-cooked with layers of vegetables such as potatoes, eggplant, tomatoes, bell peppers, carrots, and onions, seasoned with garlic, bay leaves, and herbs.

Southern Vietnam Noodle Soup. Rich and flavorful bowl of pho featuring tender pork offal, including pork stomach, intestines, and liver, paired with fresh, high-quality imported beef. Our broth, slow-cooked with premium beef bones, delivers a deep, aromatic taste that perfectly complements the hearty meatballs (bo vien) and delicate noodles. This hearty soup is filled with vibrant beets, cabbage, and a medley of vegetables, delivering the perfect balance of sweet, tangy, and savory flavors—a true taste of Ukrainian tradition and comfort.
